title: Doirdon Magnetic Drawing Board for Kids & Children 5-10 Years Large-Size, Fun Magnetic Board with Colourful Beads and Drawing Stylus (Advanced Edition)
description: This product is an entertaining magnetic toy that can help children improve their focus and creativity. Children can use magnetic pen to draw various patterns on the large-size drawing board. The toy is safe and durable and has a wealth of patterns that can continue to attract children's attention. If your child is between 5 and 10, please choose this large-size drawing board.
feature_bullets: [" 【Bigger & Better】:The large size magnetic drawing board has 15*11 dots. It meets the drawing needs of older children (5-10 years). By moving these colorful magnetic beads around on the doodle board, kids will have fun spreading their imaginations and creating their own unique patterns."," 【Lightweight and portable】: With the same number of pixels, our magnetic suction board has been optimized to weigh 1.2lb, making it easy for children to carry. In addition, a pen with a fixed rope will not be easily lost."," 【Safety and durability】: The colorful chocolate beans are sealed inside a sturdy drawing board with a transparent PC panel, so the circular pieces will not be lost or swallowed by children."," 【20 Rich patterns】: 10 double-sided cards provide a total of 20 patterns.
